        <p>
            This module examines the relationship of the person with MS and the MS Nurse. You will learn about the psychological and social impact MS can have on individuals and their families. This includes mental health issues such as depression, anxiety and cognition as well as the impact on employment and social activities. You will gain understanding of how the trained MS Nurse can optimise the outcomes for someone living with MS.
